docs.lead_paragraph: THE BREACH OF PROMISE CASE.--The case of SUSAN MARIA LEARNED vs. ALFRED WATKYNS, for breach of promise, which has occupied the attention of the Circuit Court for several days past, closed last night, with a verdict of $3,500 for the plaintiff. There are but very few points of interest in this case, although the testimony was somewhat elab orate.
